<owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="#807f912df8c44f90b62d52a:OrganizationalMeasure">
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="#OrganizationalMeasure"/>
  <uuid rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">807f912df8c44f90b62d52a</uuid>
  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Whenever you visit a website that displays the ESRB Privacy Online certification seal you can expect to be notified of What personal information may be collected and by what means Who if anyone is collecting your personal information How this information may be used including who if anyone it might be shared with The consequences if any resulting from your refusal to provide personal information How you can access and if necessary change the personal information a company maintains How a company ensures data security quality and integrity Where and how to ask questions or file complaints</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

