  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">SCEA's consumer services department may collect additional information such as credit card, personal check information, if a consumer contacts consumer services to request repair of, exchange of, or service on, a PlayStation system. Consumer Services uses this information only for payment and payment verification purposes.</evidence>
